choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.
Sure, I can help you with that! Here's a sample meal plan for a healthy and balanced diet:
- Breakfast: Oatmeal with almond milk, sliced banana, and walnuts
- Snack: Apple slices with peanut butter
- Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and balsamic vinaigrette dressing
- Snack: Carrot sticks with hummus
- Dinner: Baked salmon fillet with roasted asparagus and quinoa
To make this meal plan even healthier, you can add more fruits and vegetables, reduce the amount of processed foods, and choose lean protein sources.
